        "value": "http://localhost:1337/*,http://127.0.0.1:1337/*,https://ideatown.firefox.com/*,https://mozilla.github.io/idea-town-addon/stub-content/,https://people.mozilla.org/~jhirsch/universal-search-addon/*"
